<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Slamaster</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-02-17 13:30:00</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>All i can say is that i got extremely lucky on this one. After getting the container and the silver ring, i was almost ready to give up the quest until i saw the plat ring on auction for 1000pp.  I immediately got the plat ring and decided to camp Mitty to get the other two rings.  I went to the temple where mitty spawns and killed her. GOLD RING!. i camped mitty for another 3 hours hoping to get the copper ring when a fellow guildmate offered me his copper ring at no charge. I put all four ring in the container and VOILA my very own paw of opolla.<BR>
<BR>
P.S. I liked this quest so much that i look forward to spending another 60-100 hours on it again<BR>
<BR>
Sarnian Slammaster<BR>
40th rank shaman of the Sovereign Guard<BR>
Prexus</font></td></tr></table>
