<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Polarize</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-02-28 08:57:42</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>If you ever have trouble getting the gold ring to spawn on High Princess Mitty, this is how I went about improving the odds.(a lvl 10 pally named Alldar helped me on this one)<BR>
<BR>
High Princess's that guard Mitty often drop the Kerran Doll. So I collected about 10 of these and placed them around in a circle on Mitty's spawn point hoping for a voodoo miracle. Low and behold, a gold ring dropped the next spawn. I suggest trying this method, as it as worked for me. (maybe I was going out of my mind after sitting in that room for 9 hours, who knows?)<BR>
<BR>
Polarize Vaporyzer of the Fennin Ro server</font></td></tr></table>
